a317ef2aa33bd95f97e3a8263","tid":1110000,"uid":205680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T11:59:32.000Z","msg":"你個嘢壞咗啊"},{"pid":"028e4c7719c00d2de7b5e83c3916d9916ce8056a","tid":1110000,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:00:57.000Z","msg":"尋晚sammi鬧得我好岩"},{"pid":"7c783ef511d1c9db1b552a09c8f041e41c61166a","tid":1110000,"uid":216021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:01:30.000Z","msg":"我嗰晚的確係飲咗好多酒，但飲醉酒絕對唔係藉口，去犯一件咁錯嘅事，我非常之後悔，好難面對自己，接受唔到自己，睇到報道之報後，覺得自己好丟臉，我覺得好錯，好噁心，好陌生。我有深刻反思，點解唔可以控制自己去犯呢個錯誤，起咗呢個貪心。<br />\n<br />\n我對唔住蔣生，我出賣咗佢。為咗區區五百萬...... 唔係山雞俾千五萬我，我係唔會過到自己良心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PzPT33o.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPzPT33o.gif&h=f263673e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79f4ba8f86b1646f30b7765d50ffe334d4d57376","tid":1110000,"uid":73536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:01:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"16b1e0990b683d42972b37d602cfb5c52f27c45c","tid":1110000,"uid":216021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:04:18.000Z","msg":"大家快啲入黎承認自己係壞咗既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5382663ff5dc5a58d61019bb905f7bdaf3de3acc","tid":1110000,"uid":64946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:09:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}